sexism in addition to the ways

01:40:46.570 --> 01:40:47.770
in which it's complicated.

01:40:47.770 --> 01:40:50.060
Because when you ask French
linguists about this,

01:40:50.060 --> 01:40:53.940
they will say, well, things are
assigned masculine or feminine

01:40:53.940 --> 01:40:57.530
not based on their attributes,
but based on how important they

01:40:57.530 --> 01:40:59.350
are, they say very proudly.

01:40:59.350 --> 01:41:01.720
And so since the
vagina is so important,

01:41:01.720 --> 01:41:03.910
we obviously made it masculine.

01:41:03.910 --> 01:41:05.380
[LAUGHTER]

01:41:05.380 --> 01:41:07.280
-Like like the big
mountains in Dine.

01:41:07.280 --> 01:41:08.720
-Like the mountains.

